claim.claim-text:
1. A method of conveying a command to a user using a practice system, said method comprising:
detecting movement of the user using a sensor;
randomly selecting a command from a list of pre-determined commands;
conveying the command to the user using a signaler instructing the user to propel an projectile toward a target corresponding to the command conveyed by the signaler;
activating a timer after said step of conveying the command to the user;
selecting a second command from the list of pre-determined commands; and
conveying the second command to the user using the signaler upon expiration of the timer.
